Distribution: Western Atlantic: Florida, Gulf of Mexico , Antilles, Brazil (Maranhão, Paraíba, Alagoas, Bahia, Rio de Janeiro). Eastern Atlantic: Senegal , Gabon , Congo , Angola . Indian and Pacific: Andaman Sea, Arabian Sea, Hawaii, Fiji . Adults in Atlantic founded in depths from 230 to 732 m , in Indo-West-Pacific in depths from 101 to 1251 m , the shallowest record is in Hawaiian waters at 55 m (modified from
De Man, 1920
;
Crosnier & Forest, 1973
;
Cabral et al. , 2000
).
